-- Australian Athletes Face Strict Games Travel Rules, Sports Minister Says
-- B y   M a r i o n   R a e
-- 2010-09-21T22:59:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/australian-athletes-face-strict-games-travel-rules-sports-minister-says.html
Strict rules will apply to athletes
travelling to the Commonwealth Games next month after the
Australian government received advice of terrorist threats in
New Delhi during the games, Sports Minister Mark Arbib told Sky
News today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
